### Header
  Header component
  Import: `import { Header } from 'test-client-design-system'`
  Props:
    - title: string (required) — The title text to display in the header.
    - size: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' (optional) — The size of the header.
'sm' for small, 'md' for medium, 'lg' for large.
    - variant: 'primary' | 'secondary' (optional) — The variant of the header.
'primary' for main headers, 'secondary' for sub-headers.
    - isLoading: boolean (optional) — If true, the header is in a loading state.
    - className: string (optional) — Additional className for custom styling.

